### Error boundary and wrappers

- The app root is wrapped with `@kombai/react-error-boundary` in [main.tsx](mdc:main.tsx).
- Throw `Error` instances (not strings) from components for predictable boundary handling.
- [KombaiWrapper.tsx](mdc:KombaiWrapper.tsx) is a pass-through container for global providers; keep it lightweight.

